name: Fred Goater's Tea Dance
description: Under 14s must be accompanied by an adult over 18. A max of 50 tickets per person and per household applies. Tickets in excess of 50 will be cancelled.

name: Broadway Rave - The Musical Theatre Dance Party (18+ Event)
Street Funky Disco Flashback Dance Party
description: 19+ Only Event (I.D. Certification Required for Entry)Get Ready to Groove: Disco, Brass & Beyond! May 30th | Doors at 8 PM | $15 Advance / $20 at the DoorJoin us for an unforgettable night of music, movement, and mayhem as three powerhouse bands light up the stage with rhythm, soul, and high-octane energy!The Boom Shaka Lakas: Prepare yourself for a full-on Disco Circus experience! Featuring some of Torontos top veteran musicians, The Boom Shaka Lakas bring 70s flair with costuming, choreography, and 4-part harmonies. Expect everything from funky Philly Soul to NYC Disco classics, with dazzling stage antics including roller boogie dancers, DJs, stunt performances by Feeble Knievil, and fiery special effects. When they hit the stage, its time to boogie hard.Turbo Street Funk: Bringing the streets of New Orleans straight to Toronto, Turbo Street Funk deliver a fiery blend of brass-rock, funk, and Top 40 hits with their signature twist. Known for turning any venue into a dance floor, their high-energy, horn-driven sound will have you on your feet and grooving all night long.The Backstage Pass Band: With polish, professionalism, and pure musical magic, The Backstage Pass Band knows how to set the tone for an amazing night. Their dynamic repertoire covers everything from classic hits to modern jams, transforming every performance into a spellbinding experience you wont forget.Dont miss this triple-bill event that promises big sound, big vibes, and big fun.Grab your tickets early and get ready to dance, sing, and celebrate the power of live music!*El Mocambo is a fully accessible venue*
venue: The Starlight Room at The El Mocambo

name: Zumba Clubnight for Cancer
description: Legal Age 19+ (Valid Photo I.D. Required)Get ready for a high-energy night of fun with the Zumba Vancouver Crew! Join our incredible instructors for a sweaty Zumba party Class raising funds for cancer research. Dance to the beats of a live DJ, enjoy exciting door prizes, drinks, and keep the party going after the class ends. Its all for an amazing causeand a night you wont want to miss! Zumba Vancouver has been teaching classes and special events like Zumba at Canada Place for 17 years. www.zumbavancouver.ca

name: DANCE THE DECADES
description: Chop Suey Presents:DANCE THE DECADES!A Through-The-Decades Dance Party!1950s - 2020s POP HITS!50s & 60s = 9pm - 10pm70s & 80s = 10pm - 11pm90s & 2000s = 11pm - midnight2010s & 2020s = midnight - 1amDecade Shuffle = 1am - 2am

name: Day Fever
description: Coming to Day Fever? Request your favourite song before you arrive: https://dayfever.os.fan/day-fever-song-request The countries biggest day time disco has got people partying all across the UK and Ireland and with more cities being added all the time it's clear that you guys love to dance the day away! With perfect party music, personally curated by Jon McClure of Reverend and the Makers and Vicky McClure, Jonny Owen and the gang it's time you joined the Day Fever Family! Follow DAY FEVER on Facebook, Instagram, TikTok and X - @DAYFEVERUK Security â€“ Bag Policy: Large bags including rucksacks are not allowed. There are no facilities to leave large bags or luggage. If you really have to bring a bag â€“ and its preferable you dont, please make sure its small. Only one small bag per person is permitted and it must not be bigger than A4 size. name: DESMADRE w/ DJ Guari + J. Espinosa + Nate Rioz
description: WELCOME TO DESMADRE - a night of messy and beautiful chaos at Crybaby in the heart of Oakland. For those looking for a night of Reggaeton, Dembow, Moombahton, Corridos, Latin Dance, y ms, youre in for a treat. Pull up to experience a night of ratcheton and down and dirty dancing -- only at Desmadre can you get your fix of all latin dance, all night.Djs: DJ Guari + J. Espinosa + Nate RiozCome through to get your perreo on!Happy hour drink specials first hour! :)21+

name: 50 Years of Hip Hop: Video Dance Party ft. DJ Requiem
description: Doors at 8pm | Show at 9pm Ages 18+ CASHLESS VENUE - The Blue Note services all credit and debit payments only. No cash accepted. General Admission tickets have access to the First Floor or a Balcony Seat and are available on a first come first serve basis. Bags (max size 12" x 6" x 12") are allowed and will be searched upon entry. Exceptions will be made for necessary medical equipment and bags for nursing mothers. We encourage you to pack light with only the necessities to make the entry process as smooth as possible Advance tickets can be purchased online or at The Blue Note box office. Once the doors have opened, if tickets are still available, they can be purchased at The Blue Note.

name: RED Vol. 8: ROMA (18+)
description: Door/Show 8pm Picture this: You are a victorious warrior (think Gladiator), fresh from the battlefield after a long, hard fight. Now, you stand with your lover, overlooking the majestic remnants of Rome, the city that has witnessed both triumph and tragedy. The air is charged with excitement, the music pulses through your veins, and the night is yours to conquer. As the night unfolds, let the rhythm of the music by International DJ J Warren and the energy of the crowd sweep you away. Embrace the passion and allure of ancient Rome, where the past and present blend into a timeless celebration of love, unity, and freedom. RED Vol VIII: ROMA is more than just a party, its an experience-a journey through time where you and your lover(s) can revel in the glory of the night. Join us for this unforgettable celebration, where every beat, every dance, and every moment is part of your victory. Do not miss the chance to be part of this epic event-where ancient history meets modern-day magic

name: Afrobeats to the World
description: This event is 18 and over. Any ticket holder unable to present valid identification indicating that they are at least 18 years of age will not be admitted to this event, and will not be eligible for a refund. You must bring your valid ID to pick up tickets. By clicking the "Place Order" button on the Payment page, you are agreeing to the TicketWeb Purchase Policy and Privacy Notice. I also understand and agree that all sales are final. There are no refunds unless the event is cancelled or postponed. I understand that some venues may have age restrictions or ask for a small additional cash gratuity fee at the door for those under 21. Please check the show info for details Your payment will be processed Dance at your own risk. By participating on the venue dance floor you assume all risks associated with doing so and & release the venue and promoter from any liability in the event of injury, bodily harm or illness.

name: Planet Perreo - event is 18 & older
description: Welcome to Planet Perreo, where the pulse of Reggaeton meets the mystery of the cosmos! Our touring dance party is not just an event; it's an extraterrestrial journey through Perreo. As we tour across The US, we bring a unique, alien-themed party atmosphere that's out of this world, literally. Are you ready to experience the ultimate party universe? Planet Perreo is touring America now, bringing the heat of Reggaeton to your doorstep. Grab your tickets, invite your friends, and prepare for an unforgettable night where music, dance, and cosmic wonder collides. This event is 18 & older, a valid picture ID with birthdate may be needed for entry. The Mercury Ballroom is a standing room venue, all tickets are General Admission unless otherwise stated. Music starts with doors at 8pm.
